TO RUN THE PROGRAM:
In LINUX:
Open Terminal in the directory containing the directory Assignment1 which contains the .java files
Run ./Assignment1/buildAndRun2.0.bash {}

OR, if the script does not work,
Open Terminal in the directory containing the directory Assignment1 which contains the .java files
run javac ./Assignment1/*.java
run java -cp . Assignment1.Driver

In WINDOWS:
Open Terminal in the directory containing the directory Assignment1 which contains the .java files
run javac ./Assignment1/*.java
run java -cp . Assignment1.Driver


The Game has been tested on:
JAVA:

java 18.0.1.1 2022-04-22
Java(TM) SE Runtime Environment (build 18.0.1.1+2-6)
Java HotSpot(TM) 64-Bit Server VM (build 18.0.1.1+2-6, mixed mode, sharing)


openjdk 11.0.28 2025-07-15
OpenJDK Runtime Environment (build 11.0.28+6-post-Ubuntu-1ubuntu122.04.1)
OpenJDK 64-Bit Server VM (build 11.0.28+6-post-Ubuntu-1ubuntu122.04.1, mixed mode, sharing)


Windows 11(own machine)
Ubuntu 22.04(own machine) 
Ubuntu (Labnet) 
